foodMenu.fdesc: Cheese Pizza. Although a Margherita pizza is technically a cheese pizza, a 'regular cheese pizza' is a more basic meal with just tomato sauce topped with cheese. Typically a cheese pizza will also use mozzarella but other cheeses such as parmesan may also be mixed in the toppings.
